      <a href="#">
        <span class="underline hover:text-orange-400">Sign up</span> to log the virus in your local community.
      </a>

      <p class="text-gray-400 pt-2 px-4 text-sm">Use trustworthy data sources to log daily case numbers/deaths in your local community.</p>
    </li>
    <li class="mt-4">
